# Canonical portal repository

This folder is the **standalone** Next.js app for **[BlueTeamAfrica/blueteam-portal](https://github.com/BlueTeamAfrica/blueteam-portal.git)**. **`origin`** must stay `https://github.com/BlueTeamAfrica/blueteam-portal.git` (or the SSH equivalent).

## After portal changes

1. Run checks from this directory (e.g. `npm run build` when appropriate).
2. **Commit and push to `origin main`** (or the branch the user names). Do not satisfy “portal is done” with a push only to the `blueteam` monorepo unless the user explicitly asks.

## Monorepo copy

If edits were made under `blueteamafrica/blueteam-portal/` in another workspace, sync into this clone (excluding `.git`, `node_modules`, `.next`, `.env.local`) before committing here.
